4.  Now that we have heard both sides of the story the picture becomes a little clearer.  First, what Trist posted originally is clearly one sided and only a small portion of the story.  He never mentions why he ordered Radiant to make a rush upon zoning in.  He never mentions that an ADD officer attempted negotiations other than to say Banelion told him ADD was going to engage.  Bane said this AFTER he attempted negotiations, was ignored and Radiant zoned in.<br>
